 Cheat Mode:

 During play press and hold down the [Alt] key and type in any of the
 following numbers for differnt effects:

 370 = Outlaw stag hunting.
 371 = Outlaw merry men.
 372 = Outlaw Robin Hood.
 373 = Put a price on Robin's head.
 441 = Cycle through seasons.
 213 = Move to island near little John.
