 666 = Cause a church service.
 222 = ?????.


@ENDNODE

@NODE AfterBurner "Afterburner"


 Cheat Mode:

 Pause the game and type in `TOGETHER IN ELECTRIC DREAMS'.
 Once you've typed it in you should here a digitised voice saying WOW.
 You can now press the following keys during play:

 [G] = More missiles.
 [T] = Less missiles.
 [N] = Extra lives.
 [<] = Go down a stage.
 [>] = Go up a stage.


@ENDNODE

@NODE AfterTheWar "After The War"


 Level Code:

 Stage 2: 101069


 Cheat Mode:

 On stage 1 hold down [Alt], [B] and [1] for infinite energy and time.
 On stage 2 hold down [Alt], [M] and [1] for infinite energy and time.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Agony "Agony"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the title screen type in `FANTASY'. The music will become slightly
 louder and the power light will dim to indicate that you've activated
 the cheat mode. Now during the game you can press:

 [F1]     = Sword below owl.
 [F2]     = Sword above owl.
 [F3]     = Enlarge bullets & 10.000 extra points.
 [F4]     = Extra life.
 [Return] = Level skip.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Alien3 "Alien 3"


 Cheat Mode:

 To skip levels, go to the Options Screen, select Hard Level and six
 credits, then start. Now when you want to skip levels press [Space]
 and [N] simultaneously.


