@NODE Apocalypse "Apocalypse"


 Cheat Mode:

 The cheat mode is FRANK backwards and it must be entered during play
 as follows:

 Press and hold [K], press and hold [N] while holding [K].
 Release [K], press and hold [A] while holding [N].
 Release [N], press and hold [R] while holding [A].
 Release [A], press and hold [F] while holding [R].
 Release [R], release [F].

 You are now invulnerable to enemy fire. At the beginning of each level
 the cheat is disabled and must be reentered to reenable it.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Aquaventura "Aquaventura"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the options screen hold down [Ctrl] and [F10] and then press fire to
 start. You can now skip levels by pressing [L] and skip to the tunnel
 section by pressing [T].


@ENDNODE

@NODE ArabianNights "Arabian Nights"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the title screen type `SIMEON'. The bottom half of the screen will
 then flash red to acknowledge you have activated the cheat mode.
 You will now be able to press and hold down the left [Amiga] key during
 the game to become invincible. You can also press and hold down [K] on
 the kart section to maintain top speed.
 Also try any of the following ingame keys for different effects:

 [Tab] = Level skip.
 [F10] = Pal/NSTC.
 [E]   = English text.
 [F]   = Francais text.
 [D]   = Deutsch text.
 [I]   = Italiano text.
 [H]   = Slow mode.


@ENDNODE

@NODE ArcherMacleansPool " Archer Macleans Pool"


 Cheat Mode:

 Go into trick shot mode, then type in the code `V12F'.
 You will now hear a double click. Now go into the demo menu and you will
 see a new option. This will allow you to select and watch any player to
 see how good they are.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Archipelagos "Archipelagos"


 Cheat Mode:

 When asked to select an Archipelago, choose 8421 and press the [Return]
 key twice. You can now select any island from 1 to 9999 to play.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Arkanoid "Arkanoid"


 Cheat Mode:

 When playing the game pause it and type `DSIMAGIC'. Now unpause the game
 and catch the pill that is falling down from the centre of the screen.
 You can now press any of the following keys:

 [B] = Exit Open.
 [C] = Magnetic Bat.
 [D] = Three Ball Split.
 [E] = Extended Bat.
 [F] = Final Screen.
 [L] = Lazer Bat.
 [P] = Extra Bat.
 [S] = Slow Ball.

 And you can also press [Enter] on the numeric keypad to skip levels.
 Or for an extra 33 levels press [F3] for a one player game and [F4] for a
 two player game instead of [F1] and [F2].


@ENDNODE

@NODE Armour-Geddon "Armour-Geddon"


 Cheat Mode:

 When in the HQ, access the messages screen.
 Move the arrow so it points to the first letter of the message "DAY 1"
 which is highlighted in yellow. Now hold down the [Escape] key and press
 the left mouse button, the message "YOU WOULDN'T LET IT LIE!" will
 appear. This indicates that the cheat mode is now active.
 This makes your craft invincible and the supplies of firepower and fuel
 unlimited. To turn the cheat mode off simply access the message screen
 again and point the arrow to the first letter of the message highlighted
 in yellow. Press and hold down the [Esc] key and click the left mouse
 button, the message "LOOK AT THE SIZE OF THAT SAUSAGE" will appear,
 the cheat mode is now off.
 You can also enter an objet editor which allows every item in
 Armour-Geddon to be viewed. To enter the editor simply move the arrow to
 the top left corner of the secondry title screen and hold down the left
 [Shift] key and press the left mouse button, you will now be greeted by a
 vertical line. This is an object from Armour-Geddon, to view more
 interesting ones try using the arrow keys. Press [F9] and [F10] to zoom
 in and out of the objects and [7] and [8] and both the brackets on the
 numeric keypad to rotate them. To exit the object editor simply press
 [Escape] or any key from [F1] to [F6] to access the relevant section,
 eg, the HQ screen.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Assassin "Assassin"


 Cheat Mode:

 On mission one run right until you come to the first tree.
 Climb up the left side of the tree until you can go no further.
 Now hold down the left [Shift] key and type `NICEVIEWFROMUPHEREMATE'.
 The screen will flash indicating that the cheat mode is active.
 During this process the game will have automaticly paused it self so
 press [P] to unpause.
 You are now free to press any of the following keys during play:

 [C]        = Continue.
 [E]        = Skip to end of level.
 [S]        = Extra time.
 [W]        = Extra weaponry.
 [1] to [6] = Level select.


 Also, try entering any of the following onto the highscore table for
 differnt messages:

 `Ailen Breed'
 `Assassin'
 `Body Blows'
 `Overdrive'
 `Project X'
 `Psionic Systems'
 `Superfrog'
 `The one and only'


@ENDNODE

