@NODE CoolSpot "Cool Spot"


 Cheat Mode:

 Pause the game and using the joystick create the word COOL as follows:

 Left, Down, Right, Fire     = C
 Left, Down, Right, Up, Fire = O
 Left, Down, Right, Up, Fire = O
 Down, Right, Fire           = L
 Up, Down, Left, Right, Fire = Return

 When you enter various letters you should here cool spot say "OK".
 If you unpause when you here this you will be warped to the bonus level.
 However, if you complete all the above movements the following keys are
 activated:

 [1] to [0] = Jump to level 1 to 10.
 [F10]      = Next level.
 [F9]       = Return to level 1.
 [F3]       = Gives 6 continues.
 [F2]       = Move spot around screen.


