@ENDNODE

@NODE FighterBomber "Fighter Bomber"


 Cheat Mode:

 Enter your name in as `BUCKAROO' and the computer will respond by
 displaying: "Oooooh Nooooo its a Buckaroo" and allowing you access to
 any of the sixteen missions. You can also press [D] at any time to be
 transported to the next waypoint. Unfortunately, it seems that this
 cheat mode wasn't included in newer versions of the game.


