 The screen will then flash telling you the cheat mode is active.
 You can now press any of the following whilst playing:

 [S] = Shop
 [N] = Next level


@ENDNODE

@NODE FormulaOneGrandPrix "Formula One Grand Prix"


 Cheat Mode:

 If you want to win the race, pull into the pits on the last lap and press
 the [Escape] key. Now put the timer on acelerated time and when you see
 the finishing posisions you will have come first.


@ENDNODE

@NODE FullContact "Full Contact"


 Cheat Mode:

 In the one player game type `QAZWXEDCRFVTGBYHNUJM' and before you've
 finished typing in the cheat your opponent should give up and die.


@ENDNODE

