@NODE GoldenAxe "Golden Axe"


 Playing Tips:

 To get an extra three lives play in one player mode but with two
 joysticks and when you lose your last life quickly press fire on the
 second joystick to get the second players three lives.


@ENDNODE

@NODE GrahamGoochsWorldClassCricket "Graham Gooch's World Class Cricket"


 Cheat Mode:

 When batting, to get a lot of runs press [P] when the fielder picks up
 the ball to pause the game. The fielder will be frozen, but your batsmen
 won't. Simply waggle the joystick and your batters will run.
 You can now chalk up a high score. When you've had enough simply press
 [P] again to unpause the game. You can also press the [Spacebar] twice
 while your bowler is running to start your bowl again.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Gremlins2 "Gremlins 2"


 Cheat Mode:

 Simply enter your name in as `SINATRA' on the high score table for
 infinite lives.


@ENDNODE

@NODE GuySpy "Guy Spy"


 Cheat Mode:

 Type `GETVONMAXGUY' and then hit [Enter] followed by [F1].
 You will now see the game unfold by itself.


@ENDNODE

