@NODE JamesPond "James Pond"


 Cheat Mode:

 Type in `JUNKYARD' whilst playing and you can now use the following keys:

 [Z]      = Level 3.
 [X]      = Level 4.
 [C]      = Level 5.
 [V]      = Level 6.
 [B]      = Level 7.
 [N]      = Level 8.
 [M]      = Level 9.
 [D]      = Makes locks dissapear.
 [Return] = Toggles cheat on/off.


@ENDNODE

@NODE JamesPond2 "James Pond 2 - Robocod"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the roof before the first door pick up the objects in this order:
 Cake, Hammer, Earth, Apple, Tap.
 Note, the first letter of each object spells CHEAT. You are now
 invincible for about 15 minutes.
 In the first room of the first door, there are the following pick-ups
 close together:
 Lips, Ice-cream, Violin, Earth, Snowman.
 Pick them up in that order (spells LIVES) for infinite lives.

 Or alternatively you could try the following cheat mode.
 At any time in the intro or on the title screen type `LITTLE MERMAID'.
 The screen will flash green to confirm the cheat mode has been activated.
 The following keys are now active during play:

 [F]        = Toggles wings on/off.
 [C]        = Toggles car on/off.
 [P]        = Toggles plane on/off.
 [B]        = Toggles bathtub on/off.
 [S]        = Save postion.
 [G]        = Goto save position.
 [M]        = Map selector (enter desination from 0 to 50).
 [K]        = Kills Robocod.
 [X]        = Goto exit pole (using X to often crashes the computer).
 [Return]   = Invincible on/off.
 [F6]/[F7]  = Toggles 50/60 Mhz mode (if you have big or super agnus).
 [F9]/[F10] = Toggle timing colours (isn't a cheat but you can do it).


@ENDNODE

@NODE JamesPond2-AGA "James Pond 2 (AGA) - Robocod"


 Cheat Mode:

 This cheat mode has almost the same effects as the normal version but to
 activate it you must type in `O.S. FRIENDLY' instead.
 The only difference being that you can now select from 0 to 55 in the map
 selector room.


@ENDNODE

