 [F4]  = Mission 2-1.
 [F5]  = Mission 2-2.
 [F6]  = Mission 3-1.
 [F7]  = Mission 3-2.
 [F8]  = Mission 4-1.
 [F9]  = Mission 4-2.
 [F10] = Mission 4-3.
 [L]   = Extra Life.
 [K]   = Extra Ammo.
 [F]   = Fly.
 [D]   = Die.
 [I]   = Flash Of Light.
 [Z]   = Remove Game Sprites.
 [M]   = Remove Game Sprites And Platforms.
 [N]   = Return Game To Normal.


 Playing Tips:

 Just before you enter the door to mission one, jump onto the files that
 are on the floor. Now jump to the far right on top of the notice board
 and press up.
 You will now find yourself in a room with a devil and four extra lives.


@ENDNODE

@NODE LionHeart "Lion Heart"


 Cheat Mode:

 During the game crouch down and press [P] to pause the game.
 Then hold [Ctrl] and the [Help] key down until the screen shakes.
 You will now be blessed with infinite lives and you can also press [F1]
 to [F10] and [1] to [5] to skip straight to any of the levels.
 And to be able to fly, simply press the [Ctrl] key again and control
 Lionheart with the mouse. To stop flying press the [Ctrl] a second time.


@ENDNODE

