@NODE MortalKombat "Mortal Kombat"


 Cheat Mode:

 There are a number of different ways to activate this cheat mode because
 all it requires is a certain number of keys to pressed a few times.
 However, the following method is the official one.
 To activate the cheat mode, when the start game/options screen appears
 type `ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTU' four times on your keyboard and a cheat menu
 option will appear.


 Playing Tips:

 Here are the finishing moves for Mortal Kombat:

 Rayden:      Towards, Away, Away, Away, Fire.
 Johnny Cage: Towards, Towards, Towards, Fire.
 Kano:        Away, Away, Fire.
 Liu Kang:    Towards, Down, Away, Up, Towards, Down.
 Scorpion:    Down, Down, Fire.
 Sub-Zero:    Towards, Down, Towards + Fire.
 Sonya Blade: Towards, Towards, Away, Away, Fire.

 To fight Reptile:

 On the bridge level you must double flawless your opponent without
 blocking and then use your fatality move as one of the various shadows
 passes over the moon. If performed correctly text will appear across the
 screen announcing the fact that YOU HAVE FOUND REPTILE !.


@ENDNODE

@NODE MrNutz "Mr Nutz"


 Cheat Mode:

 On level one, when you come to the first working teleporter, keep going
 right untill you come to the first ladder. Go up it to get a blue flag -
 it has loads of gems, lives and hit points so you can keep going untill
 you have thousands of stars and 99 lives.
 Also, on the Inca level, when you sea a fish (he's behind the first brick
 you blow up), talk to him and select:
 `Bubble Bubble? `How do you know that?' Are you an enchanted prince?'
 and eccept his offer. You can now have infinite trips to the warp zone
 even without gems!


@ENDNODE

@NODE NavySeals "Navy Seals"


 Cheat Mode:

 Type your name in as `PSBOYS' on the high score table.
 Now during the game press [H] to pause the game and then press the
 [Escape] key to skip levels.


@ENDNODE

