 Cheat Mode:

 Activate lightning, hold down the left mouse button and key number [1].
 Now release the mouse button but keep [1] depressed and the lightning
 continues but your manna does not go down.
 Also, try typing in `MUSIC' as a special code for different music and
 click on the writing that goes round the game area for special effects.


@ENDNODE

@NODE PowerDrift "Power Drift"


 Cheat Mode:

 Enter and win every race on every course except course D. You must win
 them and get a gold medal, finishing in the top three is not good enough.
 Collect all the gold medals and you will enter a bonus round on a secret
 course with you in control of the F-14 Tomcat from Afterburner with no
 collision detection.
 Do the same thing on course D and collect all the gold medals and this
 time you will be in control of the Super Hang On bike.


@ENDNODE

