@NODE Predator2 "Predator 2"


 Cheat Mode:

 Pause the action and type `YOUR ONE UGLY MOTHER' for infinite lives.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Premiere "Premiere"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the title screen type `SPARKPLUGS'. The word cheat will now start
 flashing up on screen. This gives you infinite lives and alows you to
 skip to and past the end of level badies by pressing the [Spacebar].


@ENDNODE

@NODE PremierManager "Premier Manager"


 Cheat Mode:

 By dialling the following numbers on the telephone you will be able to
 improve your team's skill.

 Number   Effect

 753423 = 99% Handling.
 250967 = 99% Tackling.
 000123 = 99% Passing.
 220769 = 99% Shooting.
 781560 = 99% Everything & Ł20,000,000.


@ENDNODE

@NODE PremierManager2 "Premier Manager 2"


 Cheat Mode:

 By dialling the following numbers on the telephone you will be able to
 access a bandit machine where you can gain and loose money, players etc.

 Number   Effect

 896610 = Winning machine.
 000123 = Loosing machine.


@ENDNODE

@NODE PrinceOfPersia "Prince Of Persia"


 Cheat Mode:

 Simply press [Shift] and [L] to skip to the next level.
 For some reason, this only works for the first three levels.
 Apparently, there are other Shift key combinations in the game so try
 other keys, you never know.


@ENDNODE

@NODE ProjectX(SpecialEdition93) "Project X  (Special Edition 93)"


 Cheat Mode:

 To skip levels during the game press and hold down the right mouse button
 and then hit the [Escape] key, the screen will then turn black.
 Now with your finger still on the right mouse button press the [Return]
 key and you will be warped to the next level.


@ENDNODE

