@NODE R-Type "R-Type"


 Cheat Mode:

 Simply enter your name in as `SUMITA' on the high score table for
 infinite lives.


@ENDNODE

@NODE R-Type2 "R-Type 2"


 Cheat Mode:

 Just pause the game and hold down the left mouse button and press [F1].
 The border will flash green and you will now be completely invincible.


@ENDNODE

@NODE RailroadTycoon "Railroad Tycoon"


 Cheat Mode:

 Goto the F1 screen and hold down [Shift] and [4] (as if creating a
 dollar sign) for $500,000.
 If this fails to work then try holding down the [Shift] key an [Y] for
 lots of money (stop at 32,000,000).


@ENDNODE

@NODE RainbowIslands "Rainbow Islands"


 Cheat Mode:

 Type any of the following codes on the title screen. When you have typed
 in the code, click up a credit and an icon should appear in the lower
 left corner of the start screen. The cheat is now in operation, though
 you will have to re-enter it after all your credits have been used.

 BLRBSSBJ = Permanent fast shoes.
 BLRBJSBJ = Permanent fast shoes.
 RJSBJSBR = Permanent double rainbows.
 SSSLLRRS = Permanent fast rainbows.
 LBSURLSL = Continue after island five.
 RRLLBBJS = Hidden food changes into money bags.
 LBSJRLJL = Permanent book of continues.
 SBBJSLSB = Increase counter size.
 BJBJBJRS = First hint.
 LJKSKBLS = Second hint.
 SJBLRJSR = Slow enemies down.
 SRBJSLSB = Increase score counter to 100 000 000 points.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Rambo "Rambo"


 Cheat Mode:

 Typing `RENEGADE' on the high score table will give the ability
 to change levels by pressing keys [1], [2] and [3].


@ENDNODE

@NODE RickDangerous2 "Rick Dangerous 2"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the high score table enter your name in as `POOKY'. When you next go
 to play the game you will have a choice of an 8 bit version or a 16 bit
 version, just push left or right on the joystick to choose.


@ENDNODE

@NODE RiskyWoods "Risky Woods"


 Cheat Mode:

 When playing the game simply press:

 [F1] = Extra life.
 [F2] = Extra gold coins.
 [F3] = Skip stage.


@ENDNODE

@NODE RoadBlasters "Road Blasters"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the starting line during play type `LAVILLASTRANGIATO'.
 You will now be able to press the following keys during play:

 [F] = Extra fuel.
 [G] = End game.
 [S] = Next stage.
 [X] = Spins car.
 [1] = VZ cannons.
 [2] = Cruise missiles.
 [3] = Electro shields.
 [4] = Nitro injectors.
 [0] = Remove weapons.


@ENDNODE

