@NODE SabreTeam "Sabre Team"


 Cheat Mode:

 During the game click on the blue print icon. On the right there are the
 faces of the four men you picked to play the game. Simply imagine they
 have been numbered 1 to 4 from top to bottom then click on them in the
 following order: 3,4,1,2,2,4,1,3.
 Now return to the game by clicking on the top left arrow.
 You will now have unlimited action moves for each player and you can skip
 to the appropriate level by pressing [1] to [5].
 Once you have skipped or completed a level you will have to repeat this
 proccess.


