@NODE SpaceCrusade "Space Crusade"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the squadren selection screen choose your team and wait for the
 shuters to close. Move the curser under the name of the team you have
 just picked. Now press and hold down the following numeric keypad number
 depending on what team you have picked:
 1 = Blood Angels, 2 = Imperial Fists, 3 = Ultra Marines.
 Now press the left mouse button four times and then the right button four
 times, blue stripes will now flash across the screen indicating that the
 cheat mode has been activated. This will give your team as many action
 moves and shots as you like during play.


@ENDNODE

@NODE  SpindizzyWorlds " Spindizzy Worlds"


 Cheat Mode:

 Load up the game as normal and select a cluster of planets to view it
 close up. Now type in `Edit' (capital E, and the rest in lowercase) and
 a disclaimer screen will appear. If you agree with the disclaimer some
 brief instructions will appear. Hit the fire button to return to the
 planet cluster and fire again to play. There will not be any scenery
 there, you can now create your own.


@ENDNODE

