@NODE SuperHangOn "Super Hang On"


 Cheat Mode:

 To activate the cheat mode you must beat the highest score on the current
 continent highscore table, Africa is fairly easy.
 Enter `750J' on the highscore table and press the fire button, it should
 now change to `....'. The cheat mode is now enabled.
 To get into the cheat mode alteration menu hold down [Ctrl], left [Alt],
 [Z] and [T] while the credits screen changes to the options screen.
 If all goes well the screen will turn black and it is at this point when
 you should release all of the keys. You will now be asked to enter new
 values for the outer and inner road turn effect coefficients using the
 numeric keypad, just repeat the same numbers that are on the screen or if
 you want an easy ride change them to 00 and 00.
 Now when playing simply hold the left [Amiga] key and you will be able to
 fire a machine gun which will distroy all other bikes and road side
 obstacles.


@ENDNODE

@NODE SuperOffRoadRacer "Super Off Road Racer"


 Cheat Mode:

 Simply hold down the fire button while the game is loading only releasing
 it when you come to the name/country selection screen.
 You will then find when you loose a race that you have infinite credits
 and money.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Switchblade "Switchblade"


 Cheat Mode:

 Type in `POOKY' on the high score table. Now while you're playing press
 one of the numerical keys (1 to 5) to warp straight to that level.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Switchblade2 "Switchblade 2"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the title screen type in `LEVEL' followed by the level number you want
 to go to and then press the fire button.
 Also type in `CHROME' to go to a sub level game like Venus The Fly Trap.
 And here are all the level codes to that hidden game:

 01: N/A    05: CLOUD  09: PAPER  13: APPLE  17: AUDIO
 02: TRUTH  06: MOUSE  10: EARTH  14: JUICE  18: LOGIC
 03: JELLY  07: HUMAN  11: SPACE  15: CHESS  19: TITLE
 04: STORY  08: FLOOR  12: GENAM  16: WORLD  20: VENUS

 Also try entering the code `CHEAT'.


@ENDNODE

@NODE SwordOfSodan "Sword Of Sodan"


 Cheat Mode:

 Enter your name in as `NANCY' on the high score table.
 This gives the player infinite lives and the option to skip levels by
 pressing the [Return] key.


@ENDNODE

@NODE Syndicate "Syndicate"

 Cheat Mode:

 On the menu screen configure your company name to any of the following
 for their desired results:

 `ROB A BANK'      = 100000000 credits.
 `OWN THEM'        = All countrys are yours.
 `DO IT AGAIN'     = Start in any country.
 `WATCH THE CLOCK' = Time goes very quickly, very useful for researching.
 `MARKS TEAM'      = Best team, 18 Cyborgs and everything researched.


@ENDNODE

@NODE TacticalManager "Tactical Manager"


 Cheat Mode:

 Type `CODE' on the main screen and a prompt will appear asking you to
 enter a code. Put in the word `CODE' again, and a list of cheats will
 appear. To access the full editor just type `EDIT' on the main screen
 without typing CODE first. You can now press:

 W = Enables you to manage any team, but make sure you have accessed the
     editor otherwise it doesn't work.

 Once you have typed W, a small green and yellow strip should appear just
 along from the logo and auto icon things, under the second logo space.
 You can now go to the managers menu and join any club. Your rating
 automaticlly jumps to that of the new team, unless you are joining a
 lesser club.
 Finally, if you want to alter teams because of transfers among
 Premiership and Division 1 teams, to maintain more accurate club records,
 instead of creating a whole new player in the editor, it is best to make
 yourself the manager of the club who bought the player, enable FREE
 transfers, and transfer the player that way. This means the player keeps
 his original ID number. For example, Paul Furlong was bought by Chelsea
 from Watford, so to enable this change, simply become Chelsea manager,
 enable FREE transfers, and approach Watford.


@ENDNODE

@NODE TeamYankee "Team Yankee"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the filling screen pop up a file and instead of entering your name
 type in `Let me cheat!' (making sure you include the capital and the
 exclamation mark). Now instead of pressing return, hit the Reset button.
 The number next to the losses columm will now be 1, and this shows you
 are in the cheat mode. Now type your name in and you can get into the
 game as normal.
 In this cheat mode there are two major facilities. If you press the
 left [Amiga] key and [W] during a scenario you will automaticly win the
 battle. And if you go to the map screen screen during the game, and
 select a desination using the mouse, then pressing the left [Amiga] key
 followed by the number of the unit you are playing (1,2,3 or 4), that
 unit will instantly go to the the destination marked.
 This cheat mode is the same for all three games in the Team Yankee
 series.


@ENDNODE

