@NODE TotalRecall "Total Recall"


 Cheat Mode:

 On the title screen (the one with Arnold Schwartzenegger's face on) type
 `LISTEN TO THE WHALES'. The screen will then flip in acknowledgement that
 the cheat mode has been activated. This gives you infinite energy on all
 of the platform levels.
