 Cheat Mode:

 Begin the game and walk along to the Soda Pop level door.
 Pull down on the joystick to enter the level as normal and as soon as
 the "Get Ready" screen apears, push up on the joystick and press the [K]
 key while pressing fire. You should now start that particular level and
 if you press the [Escape] key at any time during the game you will
 complete whichever level you're curently on.


